'Yan majalisar dokokin Wales sun damu da cewa ana iya rikitar da su da 'yan wasan mu-
Wasu 'yan majalisa sun nuna damuwa game da shawarar da aka yi na canza taken su zuwa MWP (Member of the Welsh Parliament).
Wannan ya faru ne saboda shirin da aka yi na sauya sunan Majalisar Wakilai zuwa 'Welsh Parliament'.
'Yan majalisa na duk fannonin siyasa suna tsoron zama abin dariya.
Wani dan majalisar dokokin kasar na jam'iyyar Labour ya ce kungiyarsa ta damu saboda sunan  ya yi karin magana da Twp da kuma Pwp.
Ga masu karatu da ba Welsh ba: A cikin Welsh, twp yana nufin doof kuma pwp yana nufin Aa.
Wani dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Plaid Cymru ya ce duk kungiyar "ba ta da farin ciki" kuma ta ba da shawarar wasu hanyoyin.
Wani dan jam'iyyar Welsh Conservative Party ya ce kungiyarsa ba ta amince da sauya sunan ba, amma ya nuna cewa akwai kamanceceniya sosai tsakanin MWP da Muppet.
A wannan yanayin, ana kiran harafin Welsh w kamar yadda ake kiran harafin u a Turanci da ake yi a Yorkshire.
Hukumar Majalisar, wacce a yanzu take tsara dokar sauya sunan, ta ce: Tabbas, yan majalisun sun zabi sunayen mambobin majalisar ne.
Dokar Gwamnatin Wales ta 2017 ta ba da izinin Majalisar Wakilai ta Wales ta canza sunan ta.
A watan Yuni, kwamitin ya wallafa sakamakon sauraron jama'a game da shawarwarin, wanda ya nuna goyon baya ga sunan Welsh Parliament ga Majalisar.
Dangane da taken Mambobin Majalisar, kwamitin ya fi son Welsh Parliament Members ko WMPs, yayin da a cikin sauraron jama'a, zaɓin MWP ya sami mafi yawan goyon baya.
'Yan majalisar na bayyana suna gabatar da wasu zabin, amma gwagwarmayar neman yarjejeniya na iya zama matsala ga Shugaba Elin Jones, wanda ya kamata ya gabatar da kudurin a cikin makonni.
Dokar gyare-gyare za ta ƙunshi wasu canje-canje game da yadda Majalisar ta ke aiki, gami da ƙa'idodin hana membobin Majalisar ta kasa da kuma tsarin tsarin kwamitocin.
'Yan majalisar na iya jefa kuri'ar karshe a kan sunayensu a lokacin da suke tattaunawa game da dokar.
'Yan Macedonia sun kada kuri'a kan sauya sunan kasar a wani zaben raba gardama
Masu jefa kuri'a za su yanke shawara a ranar Lahadi ko za su canza sunan kasarsu zuwa Jamhuriyar Arewacin Macedonia.
An shirya zaben ne domin kawo karshen takaddama da ta shafe shekaru da dama da makwabciyarta Girka, wacce ke da lardin da ke da sunan makamancin na Macedonia.
Athens ta daɗe tana da'awar cewa sunan maƙwabciyarta na arewa yana nuna cewa tana da'awar ƙasar Girka, kuma ta sha yin adawa da shigar da ita cikin EU da NATO.
Shugaban Macedonia Gjorge Ivanov, wanda ya nuna adawa da zaben raba gardama kan sunan, ya ce ba zai amince da zaben ba.
Amma masu goyon bayan kuri'ar raba gardama, ciki har da Firaminista Zoran Zaev, suna da'awar cewa canjin sunan kasar shine farashin shiga kungiyar EU da NATO.
