Zaɓaɓɓen shugaban ƙasar Mexico Andres Manuel Lopez Obrador ya yi alkawarin cewa ba zai taɓa yin amfani da ƙarfin soji a kan fararen hula ba, a daidai lokacin da ake tunawa da shekara 50 da samun tashin hankali da aka yi wa ɗalibai a ƙasarsa.
Lopez Obrador ya yi alkawarin cewa "ba za a taba amfani da sojoji ba wajen zaluntar mutanen Mexico" a Tlatelolco Plaza ranar Asabar.
