A wannan Asabar, za a yi bikin Global Citizen Festival a New York, bikin kiɗa na shekara-shekara tare da jerin taurari masu ban mamaki da kuma manufa mai ban sha'awa don magance talauci a duniya.
Dubun dubatar mutane za su halarci bikin Global Citizen, wanda aka gudanar a karo na bakwai a wannan shekara, ba kawai don ganin Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin burin taron: kawar da matsanancin talauci a duniya nan da 2030.
An fara bikin Global Citizen Festival a 2012 kuma yana da nasaba da Global Poverty Project, wanda wata kungiya ce ta kasa da kasa da ke kokarin magance talauci ta hanyar motsa mutane da yawa su shiga cikin aikin yaki da talauci.
Don samun tikiti kyauta zuwa taron (wani zaɓi shine sayen tikiti na VIP), dole ne mutum ya cika wasu ayyuka, kamar aikin sa kai, sadarwa tare da manyan shugabannin duniya (ta hanyar imel ko waya) ko irin waɗannan ayyukan don wayar da kan jama'a game da  yaƙar talauci  .
