"Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu bayar da gudummawa, gwamnatocin kasa da kuma 'yan kasa kamar ku, za mu iya sanya rashin adalci na rashin abinci mai gina jiki a tarihi", in ji jakadan The Power of Nutrition, Tracey Ullman, a wani taron da aka yi a London a watan Afrilun 2018.
