Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
A kalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a sakamakon mummunar girgizar kasa da kuma tsunami da ta auku a birnin Palu na ƙasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, in ji hukumomi, kuma ana sa ran adadin mutanen da suka mutu zai ƙaru.
Saboda gazawar hanyoyin sadarwa, jami'an agaji ba su iya samun bayanai daga gundumar Donggala, yankin da ke arewacin Palu, wanda ke kusa da tsakiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5.
A Palu, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga gidajensu bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ne kuma yana a ƙarshen ƙunƙun ƙunƙun ƙunƙun a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da ƙididdigar yawan jama'a na 379,800 a cikin 2017.
Birnin ya yi bikin cika shekaru 40 da girgizar kasa da tsunami.
Donggala yanki ne na gwamnati wanda ke da nisan kilomita 300 (180 mi) a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
A cikin 2017, kimanin mutane 299,200 ke zaune a cikin gundumar, wani yanki na gudanarwa a ƙarƙashin lardin.
Kiwon kifi da noma sune manyan hanyoyin samun kudin shiga na tattalin arzikin Central Sulawesi, musamman yankin Donggala na gabar teku.
Ma'adinan nickel yana da mahimmanci a lardin, amma wannan ya fi mayar da hankali ne a kan Morowali, a kan gefen gabar Sulawesi.
Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da girgizar kasa da tsunami a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, a cewar hukumar ba da agajin bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
A shekarar 1996, tsunami ya afkawa yankin yammacin Donggala, inda mutane tara suka mutu.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake kira Pacific Ring of Fire, kuma a kai a kai ana girgizar ƙasa a ƙasar.
Ga wasu daga cikin manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka auku a shekarun baya:
2004: Wata girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta auku a gabar tekun Aceh da ke arewacin Sumatra a Indonesia, a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, ta haddasa tsunami, wadda ta shafi kasashe 14 kuma ta kashe mutane 226,000 a yankunan tekun da ke gabar tekun Indiya, kusan rabin su a Aceh.
2005: Girgizar ƙasa mai tsanani ta girgiza gabar yammacin Sumatra tsakanin ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
A tsibirin Nias da ke gaɓar tekun Sumatra, mutane ɗarurruwa sun mutu.
2006: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 6.8 ta afkawa kudancin Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, kuma ta haifar da tsunami da ya rutsa da kudancin tsibirin, inda ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane kusan 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.6 ta afkawa garin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
An kashe mutane fiye da 1,100.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5 ta girgiza tsibirin Mentawai da ke kusa da Sumatra, kuma ta jawo tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 da ya lalata ƙauyuka da dama kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wata karamar girgizar kasa ta girgiza yankin Pidie Jaya na Aceh, inda ta haifar da bala'i da firgizar tsoro yayin da aka tunatar da mutane game da barnar da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka yi a shekarar 2004.
A wannan lokacin, ba a yi tsunami ba, amma gine-gine da suka rushe sun kashe mutane fiye da 100.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfi ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia, wanda ya shahara da yawon bude ido, inda ya kashe mutane sama da 500, musamman a arewacin tsibirin.
Wannan girgizar ta halaka gine-gine da yawa kuma ta sa dubban masu yawon buɗe ido sun yi zaman sunci a tsibirin.
