Ana tuhumar Saipov, mai shekara 30, da amfani da wata mota da aka yi hayar daga kamfanin Home Depot don ya kai wani harin ta'addanci, inda ya yi tsere a kan hanyar keke a kan titin West Side a Manhattan a watan Oktoba, inda ya kashe mutane da ke tafiya da kafa da kuma masu keke.
Don samun hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara dole su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya "kashe" wadanda aka kashe da kuma "da gangan" ya yi wa mutum takwas rauni, in ji takardar da aka rubuta a kotu a kudancin New York.
Dukkanin tuhumar na da hukuncin kisa, a cewar takardun shari'ar.
Bayan makonni bayan harin, wata kotun bincike ta tarayya ta gabatar da tuhumar Saipov a kan tuhume-tuhume 22, da suka hada da tuhumar takwas na kisan kai a cikin wani tsari na aikata laifuka, wanda a ka'ida, masu gabatar da kara na tarayya ke amfani da shi a shari'ar aikata laifuka, da kuma tuhumar daya na tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
