"'Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya jawo wa iyalai da abokan Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco lahani, da ciwo da asara,' in ji sanarwar.
